### Current user info
GET http://localhost:8080/users/info/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Toggle active
PUT http://localhost:8080/users/status/{{user_id}}/active
Content-Type: application/json

### Toggle inactive
PUT http://localhost:8080/users/status/{{user_id}}/inactive
Content-Type: application/json

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:8080/users/update
Content-Type: application/json

